  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Provide 500 MP3 Lifeplayers to hardship schools (2 per school) in Kenya&#xE2;&#x20AC;&#x2122;s Great Rift Valley. Most Maasai schools sit in remote areas, making it difficult to recruit qualified teachers.  With a range of educational programs for teachers &amp; learners loaded on to the Lifeplayer - such as English in Action (produced by the British Council), primary school lessons &amp; practical programs - on-demand learning access is possible.  This is an effective &amp; cost-effective way to enhance knowledge for thousands</narrative>
  </description>
